\"], ''Bulletin of the New York Academy of Medicine'', Vol. 56, No. 5, June 1980, [[New York Academy of Medicine]].\n* [https://www.census.gov Ellis Island: Blocks 9019 thru 9023, Block Group 9, Census Tract 47, Hudson County, NJ; and Block 1000, Block Group 1, Census Tract 1], New York County, New York; United States Census Bureau.\n* Further sources are available in:\n** {{cite book |last=Bolino|first=August |title=The Ellis Island source book |publisher=Kensington Historical Press |location=Washington, D.C. |year=1990|isbn=978-0-939133-03-1|oclc=23941104}}\n** {{harvnb|ps=.|Unrau|1984|pp=1291\u20131338}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Videos===\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite video|people=Encyclop\u00e6dia Britannica Films, Inc|year=1946|title=Immigration|url=https://archive.org/details/Immigrat1946|format=|medium=Documentary|publisher=[[Internet Archive]]|location=|access-date=January 20, 2009 |time=10:22 |quote=Archive film contains scenes of Ellis Island and New York City in the early 20th century.}}\n* {{cite video |people=Guggenheim, Charles (director) |year=1989 |title = Island of Hope - Island of Tears |url = https://archive.org/details/gov.ntis.ava15996vnb1 |format= |medium=Documentary |publisher=National Park Service|location=|access-date=January 20, 2009 |time=28:24 |quote=From 1892\u20131954, Ellis Island was the port of entry for millions of European immigrants. Fascinating archival footage tells the moving story of families with dreams of opportunity, leaving their homes with what they could carry.}}\n* [http://www.wdl.org/en/item/87 ''Emigrants Landing at Ellis Island''], a film from 1903 by [[Alfred C. Abadie]] from the [[World Digital Library]]\n* {{YouTube|WRNT4EaEqXc|Ellis Island: Faces of America}}, video celebrating immigrants at Ellis Island, c. 1900\u20131926\n* {{Internet Archive short film|id=gov.ntis.ava15996vnb1|name=Island of Hope - Island of Tears (1989)}}\n{{refend}}\n\n===Other archives===\n{{refbegin}}\n* [http://www.gjenvick.com/Immigration/EllisIsland/index.html The Ellis Island Experience - Articles, Documents and Images - Gjenvick-Gj\u00f8nvik Archives]\n* [https://www.newspapers.com/topics/industrial-gilded-ages/ellis-island/ Newspaper articles and clippings about Ellis Island at Newspapers.com]\n{{refend}}\n\n===Children's books===\n{{refbegin}}\n* {{cite book |last=Bial |first=Raymond |title = Ellis Island : coming to the Land of Liberty |publisher=Houghton Mifflin Books for Children |location=Boston, MA |year=2009 |isbn = 978-0-618-99943-9 |oclc = 244481684 |url = https://archive.org/details/ellisislandcomin0000bial }}\n* {{cite book |last=Demuth|first=Patricia |title=What was Ellis Island |publisher=Grosset & Dunlap an imprint of Penguin Group (USA) LLC |location = New York, NY |year=2014 |isbn = 978-0-448-47915-6 |oclc=852221914 }}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Ellis Island}}\n* {{official|http://www.nps.gov/elis}}\n* [http://nyharborparks.org/visit/elis.html Ellis Island] Visitor information\n* [https://www.libertyellisfoundation.org Liberty Ellis Foundation]\n\n===Images===\n* [https://www.npr.org/blogs/pictureshow/2010/08/20/129320788/ellis-island-then-and-now Eerie Ellis Island, Then and Now] - slideshow by [[NPR]]\n* [http://kingstonlounge.blogspot.com/2013/05/ellis-island-baggage-and-dormitory.html History and Photos of Ellis Island Baggage & Dormitory Building]\n\n{{Navboxes\n|list1 =\n{{Immigration to the United States}}\n{{New York City Islands}}\n{{Manhattan}}\n{{Jersey City Neighborhoods}}\n{{Registered Historic Places}}\n{{Museums in Manhattan|state=collapsed}}\n{{Statue of Liberty}}\n}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n[[Category:Ellis Island| ]]\n[[Category:1892 establishments in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Artificial islands of New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Beaux-Arts architecture in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Borders of New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Borders of New York (state)]]\n[[Category:Edward Lippincott Tilton buildings]]\n[[Category:Enclaves in the United States]]\n[[Category:Exclaves in the United States]]\n[[Category:Geography of Jersey City, New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Geography of Manhattan]]\n<!-- [[Category:History museums in New Jersey]] and other museum cats now contain [[Ellis Island Immigration Museum]]) -->\n[[Category:Historic districts in Manhattan]]\n[[Category:History of immigration to the United States]]\n[[Category:History of New York City]]\n[[Category:Internal territorial disputes of the United States]]\n[[Category:Islands of Manhattan]]\n[[Category:Islands of New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Islands of New York (state)]]\n[[Category:Islands of New York City]]\n[[Category:Landforms of Hudson County, New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Landmarks in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:Legal history of New Jersey]]\n[[Category:National Park Service areas in New Jersey]]\n[[Category:National Park Service areas in New York City]]\n[[Category:Neighborhoods in Manhattan]]\n[[Category:New York City Designated Landmarks in Manhattan]]\n[[Category:New York City interior landmarks]]\n[[Category:New York City designated historic districts]]\n[[Category:Port of New York and New Jersey]]\n", "name_user": "C\u00fa Faoil", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eMedical inspection", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ellis_Island"}
{"title_page": "Stefano Cilio", "text_new": "{{short description|Italian writer and radio personality}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox writer\n| honorific_prefix = \n| name             = Stefano Cilio\n| honorific_suffix = \n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| image            = Stefanocilio2019.jpeg\n| image_size       = \n| alt              = \n| caption          = ''Stefano Cilio in 2019''\n| birth_name       = \n| birth_date       = {{Birth date|df=y|1980|11|23}}\n| birth_place      = [[Milan]], [[Italy]]\n| death_date       = \n| death_place      = \n| resting_place    = \n| residence        = Milan, Italy\n| nationality      = Italian\n| education        = Graduated in Economics\n| alma_mater       = \n| occupation       = Writer, radio personality, DJ\n| years_active     = 2015-present\n| notableworks     = [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]], [[Rit Parade]]\n| genre            = Essay writing\n| influences       = \n| influenced       = \n| spouse           = \n| partner          = \n| children         = \n| parents          = \n| relatives        = \n| callsign         = \n| awards           = \n| signature        = \n| signature_alt    = \n| website          = \n| footnotes        = \n| box_width        = \n}}\n'''Stefano Cilio''' (23 November 1980) is an Italian writer, radio personality and disc jockey.\n\n== Biography ==\nThe writer, graduated in economics at [[Universit\u00e0 commerciale Luigi Bocconi|Universit\u00e0 Bocconi]] of [[Milan]], published his debut book [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adnkronos.com/intrattenimento/spettacolo/2015/06/24/numeri-uno-mode-tormentoni-nelle-classifiche-italiane-tra_ABcCxrhE7irievgYH44fJO.html|title=Numeri uno, mode e tormentoni nelle classifiche italiane tra 1959 e 2014|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> in 2015: the project has the objective to create a list of the best-selling songs into the italian charts as far as [[Single (music)|singles]] are concerned and brings the author to list 500 songs issued physically or digitally between 1959 and 2014.\n\nThe project gets good reviews on music magazines Rockol<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockol.it/recensioni-musicali/libri/964/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli|title=\u221a Recensioni {{!}} Libri {{!}} Stefano Cilio \u2013 MEZZO SECOLO DI RITORNELLI su Rockol|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> and Sentireascoltare,<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sentireascoltare.com/recensioni/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/|title=Stefano Cilio \u2013 Mezzo secolo di ritornelli {{!}} Recensione|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> also thanks to public exposure on radios [[RTL 102.5]], [[Radio Monte Carlo]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.radiomontecarlo.net/audio/183246/STEFANO-CILIO-Autore-del-libro-.html|title=STEFANO CILIO Autore del libro \"Mezzo secolo di ritornelli. Le 500 canzoni pi\u00f9 presenti nelle classifiche italiane dal 1959 al 2014\"|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> e [[M2o (radio station)|m2o]], on which a quiz with the same name is created on the program ''Mollybeach,'' hosted by disc jockey e record producer Molella. In 2016 and 2017 the book is updated in two newer versions, inserting data of 2015 and 2016.\n\nIn 2019 a new version of the book<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.it/s?i=stripbooks&rh=p_27:Stefano+Cilio&ref=dp_byline_sr_book_1|title=Amazon.it: Stefano Cilio: Libri|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> is published by music publisher Arcana Edizioni, with data updating till 2018. This editon was positively reviewed by national magazine [[Sette (magazine)|Sette]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pressreader.com/italy/corriere-della-sera-sette/20190906/283811445341208|title=Jukebox cartaceo|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref> by Radiocity<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.radiocity.it/metti-in-valigia-mezzo-secolo-di-ritonelli|title=Metti in valigia Mezzo secolo di Ritornelli|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref> and by [[Radio Capital]], which hosted the author in one of its main programs.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.capital.it/programmi/bweekend/puntate/b-saturday-b-sunday-del-22-09-2019|title=B-Sunday Podcast|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref>\n\nFurthermore the author created a popularity [[music chart]] named [[Rit Parade]],<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.leggionline.info/sta-arrivare-la-rit-parade/|title=Sta per arrivare..la Rit Parade!|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> project that allowed him to host a weekly radio chart, aired by [[Radio Italia Solo Musica Italiana|Radio Italia Anni 60]] (909.000 daily listeners)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/TER-Dati-anno-30-gennaio-17-dicembre-2018.pdf|title=Radio TER Anno 2018|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref> and by some local radios like [[BluRadio]] (16.000 daily listeners)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/RADIO-TER-dati-anno-2017.pdf|title=Radio Ter Anno 2017|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref> and Radio Shake Hit (66.000 daily listeners).<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/radioter-2019-volume-1-semestre-2019|title=Radio Ter Semestre 1\u20132019|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref> Rit Parade lists the 30 most popular songs in Italy combining streaming, download, airplay, internet views and identification data.\n\n== Bibliography ==\n* ''Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli'' (2015) \u2013 Unificato\n* ''Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli \u2013 Le canzoni pi\u00f9 presenti nelle classifiche di vendita italiane'' (2019) \u2013 Arcana Edizioni\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]]\n* [[Rit Parade]]\n* [[Record chart]]\n* [[List of record charts]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.radiomontecarlo.net/audio/183246/STEFANO-CILIO-Autore-del-libro-.html Radio Monte Carlo interview]\n* [https://www.rockol.it/recensioni-musicali/libri/964/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli Rock On Line review]\n* [https://sentireascoltare.com/recensioni/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/ Sentire Ascoltare review]\n* [https://www.eroicafenice.com/comunicati-stampa/mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli-di-stefano-cilio-oltre-50-anni-di-musica/ Eroica Fenice review]\n* [http://www.csimagazine.it/review-stefano-cilio/ CSI Magazine review]\n* [http://www.inchiestasicilia.com/tag/mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/ Inchiesta Sicilia review]\n* [https://www.capital.it/programmi/bweekend/puntate/b-saturday-b-sunday-del-22-09-2019 Radio Capital interview]\n* [https://www.pressreader.com/italy/corriere-della-sera-sette/20190906/283811445341208 Sette Corriere review]\n\n{{authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cilio, Stefano}}\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n[[Category:People from Milan]]\n[[Category:Italian male writers]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Italian radio presenters]]\n[[Category:Italian radio personalities]]\n[[Category:Bocconi University alumni]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Italian writer and radio personality}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=October 2019}}\n{{Infobox writer\n| honorific_prefix = \n| name             = Stefano Cilio\n| honorific_suffix = \n| native_name      = \n| native_name_lang = \n| image            = Stefanocilio2019.jpeg\n| image_size       = \n| alt              = \n| caption          = ''Stefano Cilio in 2019''\n| birth_name       = \n| birth_date       = {{Birth date|df=y|1980|11|23}}\n| birth_place      = [[Milan]], [[Italy]]\n| death_date       = \n| death_place      = \n| resting_place    = \n| residence        = Milan, Italy\n| nationality      = Italian\n| education        = Graduated in Economics\n| alma_mater       = \n| occupation       = Writer, radio personality, DJ\n| years_active     = 2015-present\n| notableworks     = [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]], [[Rit Parade]]\n| genre            = Essay writing\n| influences       = \n| influenced       = \n| spouse           = \n| partner          = \n| children         = \n| parents          = \n| relatives        = \n| callsign         = \n| awards           = \n| signature        = \n| signature_alt    = \n| website          = \n| footnotes        = \n| box_width        = \n}}\n'''Stefano Cilio''' (23 November 1980) is an Italian writer, radio personality and disc jockey.\n\n== Biography ==\nThe writer, graduated in economics at [[Universit\u00e0 commerciale Luigi Bocconi|Universit\u00e0 Bocconi]] of [[Milan]], published his debut book [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.adnkronos.com/intrattenimento/spettacolo/2015/06/24/numeri-uno-mode-tormentoni-nelle-classifiche-italiane-tra_ABcCxrhE7irievgYH44fJO.html|title=Numeri uno, mode e tormentoni nelle classifiche italiane tra 1959 e 2014|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> in 2015: the project has the objective to create a list of the best-selling songs into the italian charts as far as [[Single_(music)|singles]] are concerned and brings the author to list 500 songs issued physically or digitally between 1959 and 2014.\n\nThe project gets good reviews on music magazines Rockol<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockol.it/recensioni-musicali/libri/964/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli|title=\u221a Recensioni {{!}} Libri {{!}} Stefano Cilio \u2013 MEZZO SECOLO DI RITORNELLI su Rockol|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> and Sentireascoltare<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://sentireascoltare.com/recensioni/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/|title=Stefano Cilio \u2013 Mezzo secolo di ritornelli {{!}} Recensione|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref>, also thanks to public exposure on radios [[RTL 102.5]], [[Radio Monte Carlo]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.radiomontecarlo.net/audio/183246/STEFANO-CILIO-Autore-del-libro-.html|title=STEFANO CILIO Autore del libro \"Mezzo secolo di ritornelli. Le 500 canzoni pi\u00f9 presenti nelle classifiche italiane dal 1959 al 2014\"|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> e [[M2o (radio station)|m2o]], on which a quiz with the same name is created on the program ''Mollybeach,'' hosted by disc jockey e record producer Molella. In 2016 and 2017 the book is updated in two newer versions, inserting data of 2015 and 2016.\n\nIn 2019 a new version of the book<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.amazon.it/s?i=stripbooks&rh=p_27:Stefano+Cilio&ref=dp_byline_sr_book_1|title=Amazon.it: Stefano Cilio: Libri|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref> is published by music publisher Arcana Edizioni, with data updating till 2018. This editon was positively reviewed by national magazine [[Sette_(magazine)|Sette]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pressreader.com/italy/corriere-della-sera-sette/20190906/283811445341208|title=Jukebox cartaceo|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref>, by Radiocity<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.radiocity.it/metti-in-valigia-mezzo-secolo-di-ritonelli|title=Metti in valigia Mezzo secolo di Ritornelli|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref> and by [[Radio Capital]], which hosted the author in one of its main programs<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.capital.it/programmi/bweekend/puntate/b-saturday-b-sunday-del-22-09-2019|title=B-Sunday Podcast|access-date=22 October 2019}}</ref>.\n\nFurthermore the author created a popularity [[music chart]] named [[Rit Parade]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.leggionline.info/sta-arrivare-la-rit-parade/|title=Sta per arrivare..la Rit Parade!|access-date=28 June 2019}}</ref>, project that allowed him to host a weekly radio chart, aired by [[Radio Italia Solo Musica Italiana|Radio Italia Anni 60]] (909.000 daily listeners)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/TER-Dati-anno-30-gennaio-17-dicembre-2018.pdf|title=Radio TER Anno 2018|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref> and by some local radios like [[BluRadio]] (16.000 daily listeners)<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/wp-content/uploads/2018/01/RADIO-TER-dati-anno-2017.pdf|title=Radio Ter Anno 2017|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref> and Radio Shake Hit (66.000 daily listeners)<ref>{{Cite web|url= https://www.tavoloeditoriradio.it/radioter-2019-volume-1-semestre-2019|title=Radio Ter Semestre 1\u20132019|access-date=22 October 2019 }}</ref>. Rit Parade lists the 30 most popular songs in Italy combining streaming, download, airplay, internet views and identification data.\n\n== Bibliography ==\n* ''Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli'' (2015) \u2013 Unificato\n* ''Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli \u2013 Le canzoni pi\u00f9 presenti nelle classifiche di vendita italiane'' (2019) \u2013 Arcana Edizioni\n\n== See also ==\n* [[Mezzo Secolo Di Ritornelli]]\n* [[Rit Parade]]\n* [[Record chart]]\n* [[List of record charts]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n* [https://www.radiomontecarlo.net/audio/183246/STEFANO-CILIO-Autore-del-libro-.html Radio Monte Carlo interview]\n* [https://www.rockol.it/recensioni-musicali/libri/964/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli Rock On Line review]\n* [https://sentireascoltare.com/recensioni/stefano-cilio-mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/ Sentire Ascoltare review]\n* [https://www.eroicafenice.com/comunicati-stampa/mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli-di-stefano-cilio-oltre-50-anni-di-musica/ Eroica Fenice review]\n* [http://www.csimagazine.it/review-stefano-cilio/ CSI Magazine review]\n* [http://www.inchiestasicilia.com/tag/mezzo-secolo-di-ritornelli/ Inchiesta Sicilia review]\n* [https://www.capital.it/programmi/bweekend/puntate/b-saturday-b-sunday-del-22-09-2019 Radio Capital interview]\n* [https://www.pressreader.com/italy/corriere-della-sera-sette/20190906/283811445341208 Sette Corriere review]\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cilio, Stefano}}\n[[Category:1980 births]]\n[[Category:People from Milan]]\n[[Category:Italian male writers]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Italian radio presenters]]\n[[Category:Italian radio personalities]]\n[[Category:Bocconi University alumni]]\n", "name_user": "Ser Amantio di Nicolao", "label": "safe", "comment": "add authority control", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stefano_Cilio"}
