978-0-520-26250-8}}; [https://www.h-net.org/reviews/showrev.php?id=34658 online review]\n* {{cite book |year=1971 |publisher=Stein and Day |title=The San Francisco Earthquake |author1=Thomas, Gordon |author2=Witts, Max Morgan |lastauthoramp=yes |isbn=978-0-8128-1360-9 |oclc=154735 |url=https://archive.org/details/sanfranciscoeart00thom }}\n* Winfield, P.H., ''The Charter of San Francisco'' (The fortnightly review Vol. 157\u201358:2 (1945), p.&nbsp;69\u201375)\n* [http://cprr.org/Museum/SF_Overland_Monthly_1870.html ''San Francisco'' (article)] (1870) ''The Overland Monthly'', January 1870 Vol. 4, No. 1, pp.&nbsp;9\u201323. San Francisco: A. Roman & Co., Publishers\n* [https://www.newyorker.com/magazine/2013/10/14/bay-watched ''Bay Watched \u2013 How San Francisco's New Entrepreneurial Culture is Changing the Country'' (article)] (October 2013), Nathan Heller, ''[[The New Yorker]]''\n\n==External links==\n* {{Official website}}\n* [http://www.sfmuseum.org/ Virtual Museum of the City of San Francisco]\n\n{{San Francisco}}\n{{Navboxes\n|titlestyle = background: {{California/color}}\n|title = Articles relating to the City and County of San Francisco\n|list =\n{{San Francisco attractions}}\n{{Streets in San Francisco}}\n{{Neighborhoods of San Francisco}}\n{{San Francisco Peninsula}}\n{{SF Bay Area}}\n{{California cities and mayors of 100,000 population}}\n{{California county seats}}\n{{California}}\n{{USLargestMetros}}\n{{Western U.S. majority-minority counties}}\n{{Geographic location\n|Center = San Francisco\n|North = [[Sausalito, California|Sausalito]]<br /><small>[[Marin County, California|Marin County]]</small>\n|Northeast = [[Richmond, California|Richmond]]<br /><small>[[Contra Costa County, California|Contra Costa County]]</small><br />[[Berkeley, California|Berkeley]]<br /><small>[[Alameda County, California|Alameda County]]</small>\n|East = [[Alameda, California|Alameda]], [[Oakland, California|Oakland]]<br /><small>[[Alameda County, California|Alameda County]]<