a/Poubaite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/poubaite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: (lead dibismuthide tetra(selenide,telluride,sulfide))\n#[[Poudretteite]] (milarite: IMA1986-028) 9.CM.05 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3272.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Poudretteite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/poudretteite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: (potassium disodium (triborododecasilicate) triacontaoxide)\n#[[Poughite]] (tellurite: IMA1966-048) 4.JN.10 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3273.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Poughite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/poughite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: diron(III) di(trioxotellurate(IV)) sulfate trihydrate)\n#[[Povondraite]] (tourmaline: IMA1990-E) 9.CK.05 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3274.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Povondraite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/povondraite.pdf]\n#[[Powellite]] (scheelite: 1891) 7.GA.05 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3275.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Powellite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/powellite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: calcium tetraoxomolybdate)\n#[[Poyarkovite]] (IMA1980-099) 3.DD.10 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3276.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Poyarkovite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/poyarkovite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: tri(dimercury) dioxodichloride)\n#[[Pradetite]] (lindackerite: IMA2006-D, IMA1991-046 Rd) 8.CE.30 [http://www.mindat.org/min-30767.html] [no] [no] <br/>(IUPAC: cobalt tetracopper diarsenate di(hydroxoarsenate) nonahydrate)\n#[[Pracha\u0159ite]] (IMA2018-081) 4.0 [https://www.mindat.org/min-53208.html] [no] [no]\n#[[Prehnite]] (Y: 1789) 9.DP.20 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3277.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Prehnite.shtml] [http://www.handbookofmineralogy.com/pdfs/prehnite.pdf] <br/>(IUPAC: dicalcium aluminium (aluminotrisilicate) decaoxidedihydroxide)\n#[[Preisingerite]] (IMA1981-016) 8.BO.10 [http://www.mindat.org/min-3278.html] [http://www.webmineral.com/data/Preisingerite.shtml] [http